{
  "id" : 760,
  "songNumber" : 148,
  "title" : "JESUS HAS A TABLE SPREAD",
  "language" : "english",
  "capo" : 0,
  "bpm" : 0,
  "timeSignature" : "4/4",
  "hashtags" : [ ],
  "sections" : [ {
    "type" : "verse",
    "label" : "VERSE 1",
    "lines" : [ {
      "text" : "Jesus has a table spread where the saints of God are fed,",
      "chords" : [ {
        "chord" : "D",
        "position" : 0
      }, {
        "chord" : "G",
        "position" : 53
      } ]
    }, {
      "text" : "He invites His chosen people \"Come and dine,\"",
      "chords" : [ {
        "chord" : "D",
        "position" : 5
      }, {
        "chord" : "A",
        "position" : 39
      } ]
    }, {
      "text" : "With His manna He doth feed and supplies our every need;",
      "chords" : [ {
        "chord" : "D",
        "position" : 9
      }, {
        "chord" : "G",
        "position" : 51
      } ]
    }, {
      "text" : "O, 'tis sweet to sup with Jesus all the time !",
      "chords" : [ {
        "chord" : "D",
        "position" : 8
      }, {
        "chord" : "A",
        "position" : 40
      } ]
    }, {
      "text" : ""
    }, {
      "text" : "\"Come and dine,\" the Master calleth, \"Come and dine,\"",
      "chords" : [ {
        "chord" : "D",
        "position" : 10
      }, {
        "chord" : "G",
        "position" : 47
      } ]
    }, {
      "text" : "You may feast at Jesus' table all the time;",
      "chords" : [ {
        "chord" : "D",
        "position" : 8
      }, {
        "chord" : "A",
        "position" : 38
      } ]
    }, {
      "text" : "He who fed the multitude, turned the water into wine,",
      "chords" : [ {
        "chord" : "D",
        "position" : 7
      }, {
        "chord" : "G",
        "position" : 48
      } ]
    }, {
      "text" : "To the hungry calleth now, \"Come and dine.\"",
      "chords" : [ {
        "chord" : "D",
        "position" : 7
      }, {
        "chord" : "A",
        "position" : 37
      } ]
    }, {
      "text" : ""
    }, {
      "text" : "The disciples came to land, thus obeying Christ's command,",
      "chords" : [ {
        "chord" : "D",
        "position" : 7
      }, {
        "chord" : "G",
        "position" : 53
      } ]
    }, {
      "text" : "For the Master called to them, \"Come and dine,\"",
      "chords" : [ {
        "chord" : "D",
        "position" : 8
      }, {
        "chord" : "A",
        "position" : 41
      } ]
    }, {
      "text" : "There they found their hearts' desire, bread and fish upon the fire;",
      "chords" : [ {
        "chord" : "D",
        "position" : 11
      }, {
        "chord" : "G",
        "position" : 63
      } ]
    }, {
      "text" : "Thus He satisfies the hungry every time.",
      "chords" : [ {
        "chord" : "D",
        "position" : 8
      }, {
        "chord" : "A",
        "position" : 35
      } ]
    }, {
      "text" : ""
    }, {
      "text" : "Soon the Lamb will take His bride to be ever at His side,",
      "chords" : [ {
        "chord" : "D",
        "position" : 9
      }, {
        "chord" : "G",
        "position" : 52
      } ]
    }, {
      "text" : "All the host of heaven will assembled be;",
      "chords" : [ {
        "chord" : "D",
        "position" : 8
      }, {
        "chord" : "A",
        "position" : 38
      } ]
    }, {
      "text" : "O, 'twill be a glorious sight, all the saints in spotless white;",
      "chords" : [ {
        "chord" : "D",
        "position" : 10
      }, {
        "chord" : "G",
        "position" : 58
      } ]
    }, {
      "text" : "And with Jesus they will feast eternally.",
      "chords" : [ {
        "chord" : "D",
        "position" : 9
      }, {
        "chord" : "A",
        "position" : 35
      } ]
    } ]
  } ]
}